  "instructions": [
    "In a medium saucepan, whisk together coconut milk, sugar, and cornstarch.",
    "Cook over medium heat, whisking constantly, until mixture comes to a boil.",
    "Remove from heat and stir in pudding mix until fully dissolved.",
    "Pour mixture into a large bowl and whisk in heavy cream and vanilla extract.",
    "Refrigerate until chilled, at least 2 hours.",
    "Serve chilled, garnished with toasted coconut flakes if desired."
